          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Presidential Appointment of FISA Court Judges Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises procedures for appointing judges to the Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Court (FISC). </p> <p>Currently, the Chief Justice of the United States appoints judges to the FISC. This bill requires FISC judges to be appointed by the President and confirmed by the Senate. </p>]]></text>
